name: Priyanshi(choti bhagoni, meethi matthi, chutku)
greetingText: I've figured out the meaning of life: it's me, with you, starting right now. You're the sweet treat I never get tired of. I love that you're mine. That thought alone makes my entire week.
wishText: Aankhon me teri Ajab si Ajab si aadae hai, Dil ko bna de malang ye teri wo hawayeinn hai
